---
description: LLM provider implementation patterns
globs: src/llm/**
---
- Providers implement `LLMProvider` in `src/llm/types.ts`.
- Config: env vars → `~/.agentic-setup/config.json` via `src/llm/config.ts`.
- Skip validation if `isSeatBased()` in `src/llm/types.ts` (cursor, claude-cli).
- Models: `minimax.ts`, `antigravity.ts`, `anthropic.ts`, `vertex.ts`, `openai-compat.ts`.